    Clarion Hotel San Francisco Airport
    <br><br>
        <h1>Clarion Hotel San Francisco Airport</h1>
    	  <div class="hotelImg">
		<a href="../hotels/us-ca-millbrae.html"><img border="0" src="http://images.traveltoday.net/ImageServlet?resize=60&isCrop=true&imageURL=http://image.pegs.com/images/CC/CA107/ca107_b1.jpg"></a>
	  </div>
			<p>
	  <GEO TYPE="US">401 E. Millbrae Ave.<br>
	  Millbrae, CA 94030</GEO><br>
	  <span class="rates">Nightly Rates: ( 103.13 - 103.13 )</span><br>
	          <span class="star">3 Star</span><br>
	  	  </p>
	  <br>
	  
	    	    <h2>Property Description</h2>
	    <p>Hotel sits on 8 acres of pine and palm tree resort-like landscaping. All of our rooms are done in a Scandinavian decor with old time San Francisco pictures. We offer a fitness center overlooking our garden courtyard. We offer 20,000 square feet of flexible meeting space, innovative menus and an in-house audio/visual firm. We are located just 5 miles north of an 18-hole Championship golf course, minutes from San Francisco International Airport and 15 minutes from scenic downtown San Francisco.</p>
	  	  
	    	        	      	          		<img src="http://images.traveltoday.net/ImageServlet?isMaxSize=true&resize=540&imageURL=http://image.pegs.com/images/CC/CA107/ca107_b1.jpg"><br><br>
      		    	    	    	  	  
