	    	    <br><h2>Miscellaneous Information</h2>
  	    <p>
				  &middot;&nbsp;American Dollars&nbsp;is the native currency.<br/>
								  &middot;&nbsp;Check in time is 1500<br/>
						  &middot;&nbsp;Check out time is 1200<br/>
												  &middot;&nbsp;251 rooms.<br/>
						  &middot;&nbsp;0 suites.<br/>
						  &middot;&nbsp;6 floors.<br/>
		      </p>
		
	  	  <br><h2>Directions</h2>
  	      	      	  <p>Coming North, take US 101 to Millbrae Ave E exit and make a left at the stop light. Hotel is located on the right hand side. Coming South, take US 101 to Millbrae Ave E exit and make a right at the light. Hotel is located on the right hand side.</p>
    	  	    	    	  		
	
	  	  <br><h2>Guarantee Policy</h2>
